rows.label: tev001592_MSG0001
rows.name: Doing a little sightseeing, are we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0010
rows.name: Reproach[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask the Murderess if she's instigating fights again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0020
rows.name: Propose[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask the Murderess to help you break up the fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0002
rows.name:
Your accusation wounds me, [ST:gender p1=sir p2=madam ]!
I don't start EVERY fight in New LA, you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0003
rows.name: I assure you, I am merely a bystander.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0110
rows.name: Believe[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0111
rows.name: Agree that the Murderess may not be responsible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0120
rows.name: Demand[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0121
rows.name:
Insist that the combatants should resolve
their problems with words instead of fists.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0130
rows.name: Suspect[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0131
rows.name: Say this is too much of a coincidence to believe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0004
rows.name: Your grasp of these situations is as astute as ever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0005
rows.name:
Anyway, it looks like the fight ended while we
were talking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0006
rows.name:
Dammit, Egor! You're useless!
You can't even bring home pocket change![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0007
rows.name: ...Hmm? Oh, I was just talking to myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0008
rows.name:
Anyway, enjoy your evening and all that.
I'll see you back in the administrative district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0009
rows.name: Were you a librarian in a former life?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0010
rows.name:
You must understand that everyone has their limits,
and this city offers few ways to blow off steam.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0011
rows.name:
Everyone needs a way to release accumulated stress.
Especially the common folk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0012
rows.name:

were talking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0013
rows.name:

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0014

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0015
rows.name:

I'll see you back in the administrative district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0016
rows.name:
You truly are a suspicious person, aren't you?
Or am I really that untrustworthy?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0017
rows.name: Hmm... Actually, I suppose I am.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0018
rows.name:
I'm sure a[ST:gender p1= man p2= woman ] as observant as yourself has
already realized, but I wagered more than a few
credits on this fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0019
rows.name: I'm hopeful that Egor here will be able to best Daniel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0020
rows.name:
I'll grant you that it's hardly the Roman Colosseum,
but a city with as little to offer as New LA needs these
sorts of amusements.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0021
rows.name:
Anyway, it looks like the fight ended while we
were talking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0022
rows.name:
Heh heh. You pulled it off, Egor.
That's 4,000 credits in my pocket.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0023
rows.name:
Well, I'm going home while I'm still ahead.
I'll see you back at the administrative district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0024
rows.name: Oh, that certainly wouldn't fly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0025
rows.name:
If we were to stop the fight before it ended,
no one would be satisfied.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0026
rows.name: Except for you, apparently.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0027
rows.name:
Can't you see the poetry in two men fighting with
bare fists?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0028
rows.name:
There are no guns or blades involved.
They waited until a whistle was blown.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_MSG0029
rows.name:
It's as orderly and fair a way as any to resolve a
disagreement in this world of ours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0030
rows.name: Accept[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0031
rows.name: Admit that there is some truth in the Murderess's words.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_JNK0040
rows.name: Disagree[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001592_SEL0041
